Package: PolyUniPlots
Type: Package
Title: Multiple Univariate Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-30
Authors@R: person("Herman", "Elgueta", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "herman@example.com")
Description: A jamovi module for plotting multiple univariate distributions
    simultaneously. Supports numerical variables (box, violin, jitter, density,
    rug) and ordinal/nominal variables (horizontal stacked proportional bars
    with optional diverging layout).
